Subject: Re: [T2] Trailer Hitch for a 1971 Type II

For the "Trivia Buffs", here's some info from my Dealer Accessory Book about
this hitch:

ZVW 164 268, Fit Type 2 68-71, Tongue Weight is 110lbs, Max Towing Weight is
1100lbs (w/o Trailer Brakes)(There is no Trailer Braked Weight specified
[says n/a]).  Equipped with 1 7/8" Chrome Ball and Safety Chain.

Manufactured for VOA by two companies:  Draw-Tite, Inc., or Valley Tow-Rite,
Inc.
